title: Account in process of transferring
body: My ticket on support hasnt been replied to in two days so I am going to try to find some answers here. I have another account and I can't log in, every time I try it says that my account is in the process of transferring and will take a couple minutes but this has been days. If anyone has any solutions I'd be very grateful.

replies.body: It can be a little bit for an account member to relieve your ticket and investigate your specific case.  If you have a ticket number, I'd be happy to check on your status!
someone got back to me a couple hours ago, thank you for your quick response!
